Class AROCollectorMainActivity

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.KeyEvent.Callback, android.view.LayoutInflater.Factory, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, android.view.Window.Callback

    public class AROCollectorMainActivity
extends android.app.Activity
    Represents the Landing screen, which is the main UI screen of the ARO Data Collector. The Landing screen contains controls for starting an ARO Data Collector trace, and opening the Task Killer.
